profile:
C-Star Roofing is a specialty roofing and siding contractor serving the commercial and residential markets since 1993. We are family owned roofing company licensed and insured in the Province of Ontario.

Our experienced personnel provides free estimate, roof inspections and detailed proposals. We provide high quality materials and 10 years labor warranty to ensure that you are 100% satisfied with our services. Our crews are experienced and professionally trained in the installation and repair and jobsite safety.

C-Star Roofing Inc will always provide top quality roofing job in the lowest cost. Our commitment and experience is our promise!

profile:
A company built on referrals and quality workmanship Vargas Family Roofing and Exteriors ensures clients are receiving the best quality products and service. As a GAF certified installer we can offer a top of the line 50 year warranty and excellent workmanship.
 We provide installation, removal, replacement and repair for all roof styles. Vargas Family Roofing works hard to be your solution to all of your roofing challenges. We are committed to adding quality and value to your home. 
Choosing to work with Vargas Family Roofing is choosing to protect what is important to you.
We strive to be the experts in the business and to run our company honestly and fairly. We are fully insured and licensed, our employee's are covered under the WSIB and are provided safety training. 
Our company believes in giving back to our communities that have given so much to us.  Vargas Family Roofing proudly sponsors local events and charities.
